oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: New Nashville 1780-1980 - Cedarwood Publishing - 1981 - Side A
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part one of "New Nashville 1780-1980," featuring Dan Miller (narrator), and various unidentified artists. Released in 1981 by Cedarwood Publishing Company.
